Extraordinary personal stories from around the world. Today, the Vatican priest helping refugees make the dangerous sea voyage from Libya to Italy, the miracle baby who was born to a Jewish mother in a Nazi concentration camp and the Cameroonian teacher who started her own school to pass on her passion for books. Show less